

    <div class="jumbotron">
        <h1>Song App </h1>
        <p></p>
    </div>

    <p class="p-3 m-3 border border-primary bg-light">
        This App is designed for users to input songs that they like to create a list of song and then query from that list of
        song to create potential playlists
    </p>
    
    <br>
    <form method="post" action="/songs/byTitle">
        Show Songs By Artist:
        <input type="text" name="title" 
               placeholder="Title">
        <input type="submit">
    </form>
    <br>

    <br>
    <form method="post" action="/songs/byAlbum">
        Show Songs By Artist:
        <input type="text" name="album" 
               placeholder="Album Name">
        <input type="submit">
    </form>
    <br>

    <br>
    <form method="post" action="/songs/byArtist">
        Show Songs By Artist:
        <input type="text" name="artist" 
               placeholder="Artist's Name">
        <input type="submit">
    </form>
    <br>

    <br>
    <form method="post" action="/songs/byGenre">
        Show Songs By Artist:
        <input type="text" name="genre" 
               placeholder="Genre">
        <input type="submit">
    </form>
